<p><strong>安保账号：</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-fishbone" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6127045); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6127045&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610098797" alt="Dr Fishbone" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6127045)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-fishbone" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6127045); return false;">Dr Fishbone</a></span></p>
